Description: 1942. Russia - the only country that manages to resist the invasion of the Nazi invaders. In parallel with the fighting between the regular armies deployed covert war two secret occult services, two special military departments - the German "Ahnenerbe" and Russian 6th department of military intelligence. Armed with these units are not tanks and planes, and the laws of magic and sorcery. Ancient spell allows magicians "Ahnenerbe" cause of the kingdom of the dead spirit of the Grand Master of the Order of the Sword of the Crusader Baron von Wolf, who fell 700 years ago during the Battle of the Ice. Soviet intelligence chief, General Belov, decides to connect to the operation to counter Baron von Wolf one of its most talented agents - a fourteen-girl Nadia, who is from the afterlife of their dead friends - pioneer heroes who were executed by the Nazis at the beginning of the war ...
